---
import ServiceLayout from '@layouts/ServiceLayout.astro';
---

<ServiceLayout
  title="Hand-Painted Mug Creation"
  description="Paint your own coffee mug - the perfect personal keepsake in Centerville, TN. Custom mugs make great gifts!"
  price="$10-15 per mug"
  duration="45 minutes to 1.5 hours"
  location="Centerville, TN"
  keywords="hand-painted mugs, custom mugs, pottery painting, mug decorating, Centerville"
>
  <section slot="overview">
    <h2>Hand-Painted Mug Creation - Centerville, TN</h2>
    <p>Create a personalized, hand-painted coffee mug that's both beautiful and functional. Whether you're making a gift for someone special or treating yourself, our Hand-Painted Mug Creation experience at Made @ The Local lets you design a custom mug that's uniquely yours.</p>

    <h3>The Experience</h3>
    <p>You'll select a quality ceramic mug and transform it into a personal work of art. Using professional ceramic paints, you can paint anything you imagine—your initials, a favorite quote, a meaningful design, or abstract patterns. Our instructors provide guidance on what designs work best for functional mugs, but the creative direction is entirely yours. After you finish painting, we professionally glaze and kiln-fire your mug so it's dishwasher-safe and built to last. Within two weeks, you'll have a beautiful, custom mug that's perfect for your morning coffee or as a thoughtful handmade gift.</p>

    <h3>What's Included</h3>
    <ul>
      <li>Quality ceramic mug to personalize</li>
      <li>Professional ceramic paints in multiple colors</li>
      <li>Brushes and painting supplies</li>
      <li>Expert guidance on design and technique</li>
      <li>Professional glazing and kiln-firing</li>
      <li>Dishwasher-safe finished mug</li>
    </ul>

    <h3>Perfect For</h3>
    <ul>
      <li>Creating personalized gifts for loved ones</li>
      <li>Making custom mugs for teachers or coworkers</li>
      <li>Bridal party gifts or wedding favors</li>
      <li>Birthday or holiday presents</li>
      <li>Treating yourself to a custom daily mug</li>
    </ul>

    <h3>How It Works</h3>
    <ol>
      <li>Select your mug and design idea (10 minutes)</li>
      <li>Paint your mug design (30-45 minutes)</li>
      <li>Finishing touches and glazing (10 minutes)</li>
      <li>We kiln-fire your mug to dishwasher-safe durability</li>
      <li>Pick up your finished mug in 2 weeks</li>
    </ol>

    <h3>Pricing & Duration</h3>
    <p>
      <strong>Price:</strong> $10-15 per mug<br />
      <strong>Duration:</strong> 45 minutes to 1.5 hours<br />
      <strong>Skill Level:</strong> All levels welcome
    </p>

    <div style="background: #e8f4f8; padding: 1.5rem; border-left: 4px solid var(--brown); margin: 2rem 0; border-radius: 4px;">
      <p><strong>Create your custom mug!</strong> Call (931) XXX-XXXX or email info@thelocalplace.com. Located at 111 South Public Square, Upstairs, Centerville, TN 37033.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section slot="testimonials">
    <div style="background: var(--cream); padding: 1.5rem; border-left: 4px solid var(--brown); margin-bottom: 1.5rem; border-radius: 4px;">
      <p><em>"I made custom mugs for all the bridesmaids! They were so easy to personalize and everyone loved their gifts!"</em></p>
      <p><strong>Emily B.</strong> - Nashville (45 minutes away)</p>
    </div>
    <div style="background: var(--cream); padding: 1.5rem; border-left: 4px solid var(--brown); margin-bottom: 1.5rem; border-radius: 4px;">
      <p><em>"Made mugs for my mom and sister. They use them every day and love that I painted them myself!"</em></p>
      <p><strong>Jessica P.</strong> - Brentwood (40 minutes away)</p>
    </div>
    <div style="background: var(--cream); padding: 1.5rem; border-left: 4px solid var(--brown); margin-bottom: 1.5rem; border-radius: 4px;">
      <p><em>"Such a fun and affordable gift idea! My teacher mug was a huge hit. Definitely coming back!"</em></p>
